    <title>随机数[a,b]范围推断</title>
    <link href="http://sysszcl.github.io/article/9abb1285.html"/>
    <id>http://sysszcl.github.io/article/9abb1285.html</id>
    <published>2021-11-11T14:22:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-11-13T08:07:14.999Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="获取-a-b-范围的随机数"><a href="#获取-a-b-范围的随机数" class="headerlink" title="获取[a,b]范围的随机数"></a>获取[a,b]范围的随机数</h3><p>例如： 求[10,99]之间的随机数</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Math.random(): [<span class="number">0.0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">Math.random() * <span class="number">90</span>:[<span class="number">0.0</span>,<span class="number">90.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">int</span>)(Math.random() * <span class="number">90</span>):[<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">89</span>]</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">int</span>)(Math.random() * <span class="number">90</span> + <span class="number">10</span>): [<span class="number">10</span>:<span class="number">99</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>由上推断可得出公式：</p><p>获取[a,b]范围的随机数 ： </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">int</span>)(Math.random() * (b - a + <span class="number">1</span>)) + a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
